name: Gastronaut (Austin)
description:
A ginormic black hole threatens the local planetary system! Thankfully, Gummy Gumm-Gumm, the intrepid spacefarer who also has an expanding head, is here to plug the hole before all is lost! Eat all the things. Become one with everything. Save the day. 

Made in Unity with a team of talented people during the 2020 Global Game Jam.

https://globalgamejam.org/2020/games/gastroboy-7
